'''Spindrift Station''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] base on the planet [[Spindrift]]. In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], it was [[Skirmish on Spindrift|attacked]] by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] forces, who slipped through the perimeter disguised as Imperials in [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]].

